16:17.643 --> 16:19.228
It was so cute.

16:25.860 --> 16:27.570
Drink?

16:29.488 --> 16:31.615
It's like a reenactment of that day.

16:31.616 --> 16:33.451
Sir, Teri is still in Atlanta.

16:35.494 --> 16:36.953
- They had her on the first flight out...
- Jesus.

16:36.954 --> 16:39.748
